over:text-zinc-200 transition-colors\" href=\"/\" data-discover=\"true\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-home \"><path d=\"m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z\"></path><polyline points=\"9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22\"></polyline></svg><span class=\"sr-only\">Home</span></a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-200 transition-colors\" href=\"/gallery\" data-discover=\"true\">Screenshot gallery</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 font-normal\">Settings</span></nav><div class=\"min-h-screen\"><header class=\"mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><img src=\"/images/gallery/claude/logo.svg\" alt=\"Claude logo\" class=\"h-6 w-auto object-contain flex-shrink-0\" style=\"display:block\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400\">Claude</span></div><h1 class=\"type-h1 mb-4 text-zinc-900 dark:text-white\">Settings</h1><p class=\"page-lead\">Claude offers a comprehensive settings interface with a strong focus on AI personalization, allowing users to customize their profile, work context, personal preferences, appearance (including dyslexic-friendly fonts), and notification controls.</p></header><div class=\"mb-12\"><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"relative w-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[200px] py-4 px-4 h-fit overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://media.aiuxplayground.com/images/gallery/claude/settings/1.webp\" alt=\"Claude profile dropdown menu showing Settings entry point with keyboard shortcut (⌘+Ctrl+,), along with Language, Help, Upgrade, and account management options\" class=\"max-w-full h-auto w-auto object-contain cursor-zoom-in rounded border border-zinc-200\" style=\"border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(228, 228, 231, 1);border-image:none\" loading=\"lazy\"><button class=\"absolute left-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 p-2 bg-black/50 hover:bg-black/70 text-white rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Previous screenshot\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left \"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 p-2 bg-black/50 hover:bg-black/70 text-white rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Next screenshot\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right \"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"px-4 pb-4 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-between\"><p class=\"text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400\">Claude profile dropdown menu showing Settings entry point with keyboard shortcut (⌘+Ctrl+,), along with Language, Help, Upgrade, and account management options</p><div class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-black/50 text-white text-xs rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm whitespace-nowrap\">1<!-- --> / <!-- -->2</div></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 flex gap-2 overflow-x-auto pb-2\"><button class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20 h-20 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-2 transition-all border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-400 ring-2 ring-blue-500/20\"><img src=\"https://media.aiuxplayground.com/images/gallery/claude/settings/1.webp\" alt=\"Thumbnail 1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" loading=\"lazy\"></button><button class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20 h-20 rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-2 transition-all border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 opacity-60 hover:opacity-100\"><img src=\"https://media.aiuxplayground.com/images/gallery/claude/settings/2.webp\" alt=\"Thumbnail 2\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" loading=\"lazy\"></button></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-12 space-y-8\"><div><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">What's happening</h3><p class=\"text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed\">Claude emphasizes AI personalization as a core settings feature, providing a dedicated \"Profile\" section where users can describe their work and personal preferences in natural language. This enables Claude to tailor responses to individual user contexts, going beyond basic settings to true AI customization.</p></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-3\">Patterns</h3><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-white p-4 dark:bg-zinc-900\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><a class=\"link-inline text-sm font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1 block\" href=\"/pattern/ai-personality-customization\" data-discover=\"true\">AI Personality Customization</a><p class=\"text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed\">Free-form text areas for users to describe work context and personal preferences that Claude considers in all responses</p></div><a class=\"flex-shrink-0 px-4 py-1.5 bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-zinc-900 text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors\" href=\"/pattern/ai-personality-customization\" data-discover=\"true\">Open playground</a></div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg bg-white p-4 dark:bg-zinc-900\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><p class=\"text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed\">Organized categories including Privacy, Billing, Capabilities, Connectors, and Account controls</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-3\">UX Insights</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Natural language preference setting rather than checkboxes makes customization more expressive</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Profile asks \"What should Claude call you?\" and \"What best describes your work?\" to establish context</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Personal preferences field explicitly states it applies to \"all conversations, within Anthropic's guidelines\"</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Accessibility prioritized with dyslexic-friendly font option alongside standard choices</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Visual previews for color modes (Light/Auto/Dark) reduce cognitive load</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Response completion notifications acknowledge long-running tasks (tool calls, Research)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Keyboard shortcut (⌘+Ctrl+,) prominently displayed for power users</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300\"><span class=\"text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 mt-1\">•</span><span>Settings organized into 8 clear categories (General, Account, Privacy, Billing, Capabilities, Connectors, Claude Code, Account)</span></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-base font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-2\">Design Decisions</h3><p class=\"text-base text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed\">Claude treats personalization as a first-class feature by surfacing it prominently in settings. Rather than expecting users to adjust AI behavior through system prompts or per-message instructions, Claude lets users define their context once in natural language. This approach positions Claude as a personalized assistant that understands user context across all interactions, while still maintaining Anthropic's guidelines and safety standards.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"type-h2 mb-6\">More case studies</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><a class=\"card-surface block\" href=\"/gallery/chatgpt-settings\" data-discover=\"true\"><div class=\"relative bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://media.aiuxplayground.com/images/gallery/chatgpt/settings/1.webp\" alt=\"Settings\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\"><img src=\"/images/gallery/chatgpt/logo.svg\" alt=\"ChatGPT logo\" class=\"h-5 w-auto object-contain flex-shrink-0\" style=\"display:block\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400\">ChatGPT</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1 line-clamp-2\">Settings</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 line-clamp-2\">ChatGPT presents settings through a centered modal interface with extensive controls for appearance, voice customization, data management, and parental controls, emphasizing both personalization and safety features.</p></div></a><a class=\"card-surface block\" href=\"/gallery/chatgpt-personalization\" data-discover=\"true\"><div class=\"relative bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://media.aiuxplayground.com/images/gallery/chatgpt/personalization/personalization-hub.webp\" alt=\"Personalization &amp; memory\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\"><img src=\"/images/gallery/chatgpt/logo.svg\" alt=\"ChatGPT logo\" class=\"h-5 w-auto object-contain flex-shrink-0\" style=\"display:block\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400\">ChatGPT</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1 line-clamp-2\">Personalization &amp; memory</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 line-clamp-2\">ChatGPT separates AI behavior customization from technical settings. Users pick named tone presets, fine-tune characteristics, declare profile fields, and manage inferred memories with search, deprioritize, and version restore.</p></div></a><a class=\"card-surface block\" href=\"/gallery/gemini-settings\" data-discover=\"true\"><div class=\"relative bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://media.aiuxplayground.com/images/gallery/gemini/settings/1.webp\" alt=\"Settings\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\"><img src=\"/images/gallery/gemini/logo.svg\" alt=\"Google Gemini logo\" class=\"h-5 w-auto object-contain flex-shrink-0\" style=\"display:block\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400\">Google Gemini</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1 line-clamp-2\">Settings</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 line-clamp-2\">Gemini presents settings as a left sidebar menu with categories for activity tracking, personal context, connected apps, scheduling, theming, subscription management, and ecosystem integrations like NotebookLM.</p></div></a><a class=\"card-surface block\" href=\"/gallery/grok-personalization\" data-discover=\"true\"><div class=\"relative bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://media.aiuxplayground.com/images/gallery/grok/personalization/1.webp\" alt=\"Personalization\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\"><img src=\"/images/gallery/grok/logo.svg\" alt=\"Grok logo\" class=\"h-5 w-auto object-contain flex-shrink-0\" style=\"display:block\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400\">Grok</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-1 line-clamp-2\">Personalization</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 line-clamp-2\">Grok provides personalization settings that allow users to customize their AI experience, including conversation preferences, response style, and contextual behavior settings.</p></div></a></div></div><div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400\"><span>Captured: <!-- -->December 29, 2025</span><span>Type: <!-- -->desktop</span><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2 py-1 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 rounded\">settings</span><span class=\"px-2 